      },
      "text": "# Bugs\n- [ ] NoLandCheckpoint doesn't play correct walk sfx\n- [ ] metal gate needs immediate collision change when powered\n- [ ] Music fader unscaled time\n- [ ] Skippable dialogue once read 1 time\n- [ ] Scans don't update color when same one is scanned once\n- [ ] inventory screen icons stretched?\n- [ ] biomatter force field scan is on when power is out?\n- [ ] bridge nav mesh imprecise? Chandroid phases through?",
