    {
      "height": 1237,
      "id": "e795fbced778d72d",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "# Features\n- [ ] [[Demo Chapter Select.canvas|Demo Chapter Select]]\n- [ ] build scene replay button\n- [ ] chandroid recall device\n- [ ] chandroid UI menu, select different actions (help, talk, customize, map)\n- [ ] vizualize pathfinding?\n- [ ] floating icons for blueprints?\n- [ ] opacity for chandroid silohuette setting\n- [ ] \"adjust brightness until left image is barely visible\"\n- [ ] Action log\nevery room discovered, item collected, puzzle solved, and power restored will be logged as an item\n- [ ] Save point love seats\nmonobehaviour referenced by scenestartup, which checks a scriptable object for \"doSpawn\" bool\n- [ ] Puzzle stats console\npuzzle name, required equipment, fastest completion time, etc\n- [ ] make rewire work if you select target first\n- [ ] chandroid snatchers\ndog walking robots that mistake chandroid for a dog (scary looking)\n- [ ] [[New Map System.canvas|New Map System]]",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 470,
      "x": -660,
      "y": 1380
