      "text": "# Conveyance\n- [ ] back panel cutscene\n- [ ] indication on doors to tell you if they're locked\n- [x] Make highway entrance a more obvious dead-end\n- [x] Make bridge and lift intro more obvious dead ends\n- [x] wallace doesn't want help\n- [ ] lift intro companion rewire pad should not afford pressing (surround by powered cage? phone booth?)\n- [ ] upgrade info box indication animation\n- [ ] indication before characters speak to you\n- [ ] restrict looking angles in bed\n- [ ] when no accessories, show \"No accessories unlocked!\" in character customizer\n- [ ] maidbot interior entrance: players don't know chandroid can come to you\n- [ ] notification for \"change appearance in pause menu\" after first crafted item, and maybe a ? button that will explain things\n\n\n\n",
