    {
      "height": 2180,
      "id": "28a75e18bf8ae57d",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "# Details\n- [ ] bathroom scale joke\n- [ ] \"file select\" label over file select\n- [ ] animated reactions when chandroid is commanded to the shower or bed\n- [ ] have bananas flow to edge of water during bridge lower\n- [ ] monorail cart\n- [ ] fan\n- [ ] balconies\n- [ ] gene's gadget gallery full texture\n- [ ] paintings/decor art\n- [ ] more chandroid animations\n\t- [ ] more character\n\t- [ ] idle animations\n\t- [ ] step on button animation\n\t- [ ] etc\n- [ ] drinkable cup of coffee\n- [ ] Shop shelf items\n\t- [ ] dog walkers\n\t- [ ] cell phones\n\t- [ ] chargers\n\t- [ ] anti-gravity attachment\n\t- [ ] folding wall table\n\t- [ ] litter zapper\n\t- [ ] placeable indoor conveyor belt\n\t- [ ] hovering monkey bars for kids\n\t- [ ] auto-watering garden apparatus\n\t- [ ] bass boost lazyboy chair\n- [ ] Carnivorous plants\n- [ ] Improve mall elevator aesthetics\n- [ ] make vending machine spit out soda cans\n- [ ] create console for showing battery requirements, statistics\n\n- [ ] add buildings to rooftop scene?\n- [ ] add water to bottom of drained canal\n- [ ] add camera decoration to tunnels\n- [ ] puzzle idea: in school science fair, enter and solve potato battery\n- [ ] rewrite reuben joke\n- [ ] add decals to boxes in car guy's room\n- [ ] AI art character portraits?\n- [ ] cars and boats and planes\n- [ ] cat paws neko terminal in maidbot factory",
