      },
      "text": "# Clothing\n##### Male\n- [ ] hipster hairstyle with shaved parts\n- [ ] spiky asian hairstyle\n- [ ] baseball cap - 4 designs\n\t- [ ] w/ fuzzy hair & clean hair\n- [ ] 4 futuristic headgears\n- [ ] 6 eye types\n- [ ] 4 shirts\n- [ ] 4 pants\n- [ ] 2 shoes\n- [ ] retexture labcoat as jacket\n- [ ] 3 facial hair styles\n##### Female\n- [ ] hairstyle - long one side, shaved on the other\n- [ ] ponytail\n- [ ] braids\n- [ ] sun hat\n- [ ] long hair w/ hair band\n- [ ] 2 futuristic headgears\n- [ ] 4 eye types\n- [ ] 2 shirts\n- [ ] 2 pants\n- [ ] 2 skirts\n- [ ] 2 dresses\n- [ ] cute boots\n- [ ] tennis shoes\n- [ ] Goth Boots",
