    {
      "height": 580,
      "id": "59230bdcfbdbb0f8",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Hey @everyone,\nThanks for sticking around as My Chandroid Sweetheart takes shape! I've hit a bit of a snag, though - balancing my day job and development has been tough, pushing back the release date.\n**Here's where you come in:**\n* **Patronize** - Even $1 a month can help keep me fed & independent, so I can spend more time designing and coding.\n* **Share** - Getting the word out makes a big difference. Share this post, tell your friends, or tweet about #MyChandroidSweetheart!\n* **Follow** - Stay updated with all things MCS by joining our Discord server and following me on social media @WanderStudyG.\nAnything you can do to support me will help speed up development. Let's make My Chandroid Sweetheart the best it can be, together!\nPeace out,\nTim 🤙❤️💻",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 1160,
      "x": -16040,
      "y": 1400
    },
    {
      "height": 860,
      "id": "42f83686b83c75a2",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Hey @everyone. I thank you for your patience in my development of My Chandroid Sweetheart. For the first half of this year, development has slowed down due to increasing demands from my day job and changes to my living situation. \n\nHowever, right now I'm at a crossroads.\n\nIf I can support myself through my game development, I can dedicate all of my time towards making the game as efficiently as possible. If not, I may have to dedicate significantly less time to development, meaning the game will take much longer to complete.\n\n### Realistically\n\n*kickstarter*\nIf I make a kickstarter that reaches its goal of $35,000, I'll be able to support myself on that for at least a year doing full-time game development.\n\n*patreon*\nAlternatively, if I get 150 people to donate $10 a month, I could live comfortably while working as a full-time developer.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 880,
      "x": -14840,
      "y": 1400
    },
    {
      "height": 730,
      "id": "f9fe2c7f38ed9911",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Play\n1. Upgrades + Puzzle Mechanics\n2. World (Gates + Keys)\n3. Quests (Per-area goals & subgoals)\n4. Puzzles\n5. Bosses\n6. World Gimmicks (verbs)\n7. Codecs + Collectibles\n8. Rough NPC (Dialogue + Note attires)\n\nPolish\n1. Boss Detail\n2. NPC Detail (Outfits)\n3. World Detail/Remodel/Barriers\n4. Cutscenes",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 640,
      "x": -7680,
      "y": 500
    },
    {
      "height": 620,
      "id": "a433dc0fb01d95fa",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "- tone\n- challenge",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 680,
      "x": -9040,
      "y": 500
    },
    {
      "height": 140,
      "id": "a97c5080168c31a0",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "mysterious, electronic\nspacious\n",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 360,
      "x": -9220,
      "y": 180
    },
    {
      "height": 730,
      "id": "ce3bd34a02d1334c",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Flow\n1. Create new puzzle mechanics\n2. Create a series of puzzles\n3. Test\n4. Block out new world\n5. Add puzzles to world, with metroidvania style exploration + progression\n6. Test\n7. Detail, animate, add story/characters\n8. Test\n9. Repeat for next area",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 720,
      "x": -6740,
      "y": 500
    },
